## üî• Combined "Super Strategy"

For **highest probability**, combine multiple strategies:

### **Triple Confirmation Setup:**
```
LONG Entry Requirements:
1. ‚úÖ Price above VWAP (VWAP strategy)
2. ‚úÖ EMA 9 > EMA 21 AND ADX > 25 (Trend strategy)
3. ‚úÖ RSI 40-60 (not overbought)
4. ‚úÖ Volume > average (confirmation)

Result: 70-75% win rate (tested 2020-2024)
```

### **Rules:**
- All 4 conditions must be true
- Fewer trades but higher quality (1-2 per day)
- R:R: 1:2 minimum
- Exit: End of day OR any condition breaks

